  "keyFeatures": [
    "ClawScript JavaScript-based scripting for flexible automation",
    "Vision-assisted UI targeting with magicClicker and magicScraper",
    "Cron-based scheduling for recurring automated tasks",
    "Voice command interface for generating automation scripts",
    "Multi-app workflow chaining across different Android applications",
    "On-device execution without root access required",
    "AI-powered automation script generation via OpenRouter",
    "Screen capture and analysis for adaptive workflows"
